| ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ |
| REQUIRED KEYS:                                                             |
|                                                                            |
| 1. class - The class name providing the custom implementation.             |
|                                                                            |
| OPTIONAL KEYS:                                                             |
|                                                                            |
| 1. file  - The filesystem path to the class file. If the path is relative, |
|            it will be relative to the "core.app_dir" Agavi application     |
|            setting.                                                        |
| ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ |
| PARAMETERS:                                                                |
|                                                                            |
| <parameters> element specifies a group of parameters to be passed to the   |
